summary: said it once, imma say it again...  I don’t think Harry is the type of person that feels the need to publically come out and...
body:
said it once, imma say it again…


I don’t think Harry is the type of person that feels the need to publically come out and label himself ANYTHING. I think that he believes that there is no NEED for ANYONE to come out, because being a part of LGBT+ community doesn’t change anyones personality and who they are. 

I didn’t have to come out because I’m straight, why should anyone have to come out because they are not?
